          title="1. Acceptance of Terms"
          content="By accessing or using Omnitria services (“we,” “our,” “the platform”), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service, our Privacy Policies, and any additional policies we may implement. If you do not agree to these terms, you should not use our services."
