        <ContractText
          title="3. Account Registration"
          content="In order to access certain services, you may be required to register for an account. By creating an account, you agree to provide true and complete information and to update it if it changes. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account and password. Omnitria will not be liable for any loss or damage resulting from unauthorized access to your account due to a lack of diligence in protecting your login information."
        />

        <section>
          <h2
            class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-50"
          >
            4. Permitted Use and Restrictions
          </h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            Omnitria's software development products and services are designed
            to be used exclusively by our clients and under the agreed terms.
            You are prohibited from:
