              or infringing activity.
            </li>
            <li>
              Reverse engineering, decompiling or disassembling any software or
              component provided by Omnitria, except to the extent such activity
              is expressly permitted by law.
            </li>
            <li>
              Modifying, reproducing, distributing or creating derivative works
              of the software without Omnitria's prior written permission.
            </li>
            <li>
              Sharing, sublicensing or reselling Omnitria's software or services
              without permission.
            </li>
            <li>
              Accessing or attempting to access any third party's systems.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <ContractText
          title="5. Intellectual Property"
          content="All intellectual property rights relating to the platform and its contents (including software, databases, graphics, designs and logos) belong to Omnitria or its licensors. No right or license is granted to these rights except as expressly set out in these Terms."
        />

        <section>
          <h2
            class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-50"
          >
            6. Privacy and Data Protection
          </h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            Omnitria is committed to protecting the privacy and confidentiality
            of our customers' information. Our <a
              href="/privacy-policy"
              class="text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 underline"
              >Privacy Policy</a
            > describes how we collect, use and protect personal data and any confidential
            information provided in the course of our services.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 mt-2">
            <li>
              Use customer data only for the development, implementation and
              support of the agreed services.
            </li>
            <li>
              Protect confidential information through appropriate security
              practices and keep data secure and private.
            </li>
            <li>
              Not share or disclose confidential customer information with third
              parties without their express consent, except when necessary for
              the provision of the service or required by law.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <ContractText
          title="7. Modifications to the Service and Terms"
          content="Omnitria reserves the right to modify, suspend or discontinue any part of the Services at any time. We may also modify these Terms from time to time. Modifications will be effective immediately upon posting on the Platform."
        />

