          title="10. Ley Aplicable"
          content="These Terms of Service and any relationship between the client and Omnitria shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of Guadalajara, Jalisco, Mexico. Any dispute relating to these Terms of Service or the use of Omnitria's services shall be resolved exclusively in the courts of Guadalajara, Jalisco, Mexico, unless the parties agree to another jurisdiction in a written agreement. By accepting these Terms of Service, the client agrees to submit to the jurisdiction of these courts for the resolution of any dispute or claim arising from the services provided by Omnitria."
        />

        <section>
          <h2
            class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-50"
          >
            11. Contact
          </h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            For any questions or comments about these Terms, please contact us
            at: <br />
            <strong>E-mail: </strong>
            <a
              href="mailto:legal@omnitria.com"
              class="text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 underline"
              >legal@omnitria.com</a
            >
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
